    <bpmn:serviceTask id="Activity_0pg78zh" name="Create a Catalog Task" zeebe:modelerTemplate="io.camunda.connectors.ServiceNow.v1" zeebe:modelerTemplateVersion="7" zeebe:modelerTemplateIcon="data:image/svg+xml;base64,">
      <bpmn:extensionElements>
        <zeebe:taskDefinition type="io.camunda:http-json:1" retries="3" />
        <zeebe:ioMapping>
          <zeebe:input source="your-instance-name" target="snInstance" />
          <zeebe:input source="create" target="operationGroup" />
          <zeebe:input source="sc_task" target="targetTable" />
          <zeebe:input source="={&#10;  &#34;reason&#34;: &#34;Request User Input&#34;,&#10;  &#34;short_description&#34;: &#34;Orchestrate ServiceNow User Task (from Camunda)&#34;&#10;}" target="body_sc_task" />
          <zeebe:input source="={&#10; &#34;variables&#34;: [body_sc_req_item, body_change_request, body_change_task, body_sc_request, body_sc_task, body_incident, body__custom],&#10;  &#34;result&#34;: variables[item != null][1]&#10;}.result" target="body" />
          <zeebe:input source="basic" target="authentication.type" />
          <zeebe:input source="{{secrets.snUser}}" target="authentication.username" />
          <zeebe:input source="{{secrets.snPwd}}" target="authentication.password" />
          <zeebe:input source="={&#10; &#34;operationMap&#34;: [&#10;   {&#10;     &#34;value&#34;:&#34;read&#34;,&#10;     &#34;mapsTo&#34;: &#34;GET&#34;&#10;   },&#10;   {&#10;     &#34;value&#34;:&#34;update&#34;,&#10;     &#34;mapsTo&#34;: &#34;PATCH&#34;&#10;   },&#10;   {&#10;     &#34;value&#34;:&#34;create&#34;,&#10;     &#34;mapsTo&#34;: &#34;POST&#34;&#10;   },&#10;   {&#10;     &#34;value&#34;:&#34;delete&#34;,&#10;     &#34;mapsTo&#34;: &#34;DELETE&#34;&#10;   }&#10; ],&#10; &#34;result&#34;: operationMap[value = operationGroup].mapsTo[1]&#10;}.result" target="method" />
          <zeebe:input source="={&#10;  &#34;baseUrl&#34;: &#34;https://&#34; + snInstance + &#34;.service-now.com/api/now/table/&#34;,&#10;  &#34;table&#34;: if targetTable = &#34;__custom&#34; then customRequestTarget else targetTable ,&#10;  &#34;updateOrDeleteSysId&#34;: if updateTarget != null then updateTarget else (if deleteTarget != null then deleteTarget else null) ,&#10;  &#34;fullUrl&#34;: baseUrl + table + (if updateOrDeleteSysId != null then &#34;/&#34; + updateOrDeleteSysId else &#34;&#34;)&#10;}.fullUrl" target="url" />
          <zeebe:input source="=false" target="storeResponse" />
          <zeebe:input source="=true" target="skipEncoding" />
          <zeebe:input source="=20" target="connectionTimeoutInSeconds" />
          <zeebe:input source="=20" target="readTimeoutInSeconds" />
        </zeebe:ioMapping>
        <zeebe:taskHeaders>
          <zeebe:header key="resultVariable" value="snCrResult" />
          <zeebe:header key="resultExpression" value="={&#34;crResultSysId&#34;: response.body.result.sys_id}" />
          <zeebe:header key="retryBackoff" value="PT0S" />
        </zeebe:taskHeaders>
      </bpmn:extensionElements>
